info.description:
Python Teelaunch Helper Library
    ----------------------------

    DESCRIPTION
    The Teelaunch REST SDK simplifies the process of makes calls to the Teelaunch REST.
    The Teelaunch REST API lets to you initiate outgoing calls, list previous calls,
    and much more.  See https://github.com/teelaunch/teelaunch-python for more information.
